name: RESPIRO #1
description: Respiro #1 means to breathe. It is part of a three pieces collection of video performances that explore the in and out space of the body and  existance, translating it to the sounds and the movements/motion made by body organs, the sound of nature and nostalgia. The three peaces investigate the position of feeling an outsider, to exist in the “in between” space of things, a response to anxiety, and the willing to belong.
